tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE fashion_photography_collaborations (
    collaboration_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    designer_name VARCHAR(255),
    makeup_artist_name VARCHAR(255),
    stylist_name VARCHAR(255),
    collaboration_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE fashion_photography_collaborations (
  collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  designer_name VARCHAR(255),
  makeup_artist_name VARCHAR(255),
  stylist_name VARCHAR(255),
  collaboration_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE collaboration_photos (
  photo_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  collaboration_id INT,
  photo_url VARCHAR(255),
  description TEXT,
  FOREIGN KEY(collaboration_id) REFERENCES fashion_photography_collaborations(collaboration_id)
);

CREATE TABLE fashion_photographer_collaborations (
    collaboration_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    designer_id INT,
    makeup_artist_id INT,
    stylist_id INT,
    collaboration_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE collaborations (
  collaboration_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  designer_id UUID NOT NULL,
  makeup_artist_id UUID NOT NULL,
  stylist_id UUID NOT NULL,
  collaboration_date DATE,
  collaboration_notes TEXT
);
